  "QuestText": {
    "QuestInfo": [
      {
        "Language": "JPN",
        "Name": "\u72E9\u308A\u306F\u7D62\u721B\u6012\u6D9B\u306B",
        "Client": "\u738B\u56FD\u9A0E\u58EB\u30D5\u30A3\u30AA\u30EC\u30FC\u30CD",
        "Description": "\u540C\u884C\u3057\u3066\u3082\u3089\u3044\u305F\u3044\u306E\u306F\u57CE\u585E\u9AD8\u5730\r\n\u306E\u30AF\u30A8\u30B9\u30C8\u3060\u3002\u72E9\u731F\u5BFE\u8C61\u306F\u591A\u3044\u304C\r\n\u8CB4\u6BBF\u306E\u5C3D\u529B\u306E\u304A\u304B\u3052\u304B\u3001\u6700\u8FD1\u306E\r\n\u30EB\u30FC\u30C1\u30AB\u306F\u5F35\u308A\u5207\u3063\u3066\u3044\u308B\u3088\u3046\u3060\r\n\u304B\u3089\u306D\u3002\u5F7C\u5973\u306E\u51C4\u70C8\u306A\u72E9\u308A\u306B\r\n\u5F15\u3051\u3092\u53D6\u3089\u306A\u3044\u3088\u3046\u3001\u79C1\u305F\u3061\u3082\r\n\u6C17\u5408\u3044\u3092\u5165\u308C\u3066\u6311\u3080\u3068\u3057\u3088\u3046\u3002",
        "Target": "\u5168\u3066\u306E\u30BF\u30FC\u30B2\u30C3\u30C8\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Hunting is All the Rage",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "I cannot thank you enough for\r\nworking with Luchika. Others might\r\nfind fault in her enthusiasm or over-\r\nenthusiasm, if you will. I myself\r\nwas blinded by protocol and judged\r\nher unfairly. I hope to make it up to\r\nher by hunting together. Shall we?",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "La chasse, c\u0027est tendance",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "J\u0027aimerais que tu m\u0027aides avec\r\nune qu\u00EAte pour la Citadelle.\r\nPlusieurs proies nous y\r\nattendent ! Je sais que tu\r\ntravailles dur avec Luchika et\r\nj\u0027ai presque peur de ne pas\r\npouvoir suivre. Allons-y !",
        "Target": "Chasser tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "La caccia fa furore",
        "Client": "Dama Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Vorrei che ti unissi a me per\r\nuna missione alla cittadella.\r\nL\u00E0 ci aspettano vari obiettivi.\r\nSo che hai lavorato sodo con\r\nLuchika e spero proprio di\r\nriuscire a stare al passo.\r\nAndiamo!",
        "Target": "Caccia tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Jagen ist der letzte Schrei",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Ich kann dir nicht genug f\u00FCr die\r\nArbeit mit Luchika danken. Man\r\nmag ihren \u00DCberenthusiasmus\r\nbem\u00E4ngeln; Begeisterung, wenn\r\ndu so willst. Ich selbst m\u00F6chte\r\nes wiedergutmachen indem wir\r\nzusammen jagen. Sollen wir?",
        "Target": "Erjage alle Zielmonster.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Cazando con rabia",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Te agradezco mucho que trabajes\r\ncon Luchika. Los dem\u00E1s le afean\r\nsu, quiz\u00E1s, excesivo entusiasmo.\r\nY hasta a m\u00ED me ceg\u00F3 el protocolo,\r\ny la juzgu\u00E9 injustamente.\r\nQuiz\u00E1 pueda disculparme cazando\r\nlos tres juntos. \u00BFQu\u00E9 te parece?",
        "Target": "Caza todos los objetivos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0430 \u2014 \u0432 \u043C\u043E\u0434\u0435",
        "Client": "\u0420\u044B\u0446\u0430\u0440\u044C \u0424\u0438\u043E\u0440\u0430\u0439\u043D\u0430",
        "Description": "\u0423 \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F \u0435\u0441\u0442\u044C \u0437\u0430\u0434\u0430\u043D\u0438\u0435 \u0432\r\n\u0426\u0438\u0442\u0430\u0434\u0435\u043B\u0438, \u0438 \u043C\u043D\u0435 \u043D\u0443\u0436\u043D\u0430 \u0432\u0430\u0448\u0430\r\n\u043F\u043E\u043C\u043E\u0449\u044C. \u0422\u0430\u043C \u043D\u0430\u0441 \u0436\u0434\u0435\u0442 \u043D\u0435\u043C\u0430\u043B\u043E\r\n\u0432\u0440\u0430\u0433\u043E\u0432! \u0417\u043D\u0430\u044E, \u0432\u044B \u0441 \u041B\u0443\u0447\u0438\u043A\u043E\u0439\r\n\u0440\u0430\u0431\u043E\u0442\u0430\u043B\u0438 \u0432 \u043F\u043E\u0442\u0435 \u043B\u0438\u0446\u0430, \u0438, \u0435\u0441\u043B\u0438\r\n\u0447\u0435\u0441\u0442\u043D\u043E, \u044F \u043D\u0435 \u0445\u043E\u0447\u0443 \u043F\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438\r\n\u0437\u0430\u0434\u043D\u0438\u0445. \u0422\u0430\u043A \u0447\u0442\u043E \u2014 \u0432\u043F\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0434!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0432\u0441\u0435 \u0446\u0435\u043B\u0438",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Polowanie jest na topie",
        "Client": "Pani Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Czy b\u0119dziesz mi towarzyszy\u0107\r\npodczas zadania w Cytadeli?\r\nJest tam wiele potwor\u00F3w!\r\nWiem o twojej ci\u0119\u017Ckiej pracy \r\nLuchik\u0105 i szczerze si\u0119 martwi\u0119,\r\nczy nie zostan\u0119 w tyle.\r\nDalej! Ruszamy!",
        "Target": "Upoluj wszystkie cele",
        "Fail": "Nagroda r\u00F3wna 0 lub koniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "F\u00FAria na Ca\u00E7ada",
        "Client": "Dama Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Gostaria que voc\u00EA se juntasse\r\na mim numa miss\u00E3o no Forte.\r\nV\u00E1rios alvos nos esperam por\r\nl\u00E1! Sei como voc\u00EA tem dado duro\r\ncom a Luchika e, sinceramente,\r\nme preocupo de conseguir\r\nacompanhar. Ent\u00E3o, vamos!",
        "Target": "Cace todos os monstros-alvo",
        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
      },
      {
        "Language": "KOR",
        "Name": "\uC0AC\uB0E5\uC740 \uD718\uD669\uCC2C\uB780\uD558\uAC8C",
        "Client": "\uC655\uAD6D \uAE30\uC0AC \uD53C\uC624\uB808\uB124",
